g src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aae49b4bfce884a2f0132c56f600b0307612bf35","tid":2347101,"uid":189222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b517f138cad61d927c7c0436b91fcc847ae9e01d","tid":2347101,"uid":23069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0bf72c88db6d2780b4e9a75b9db3dfb20006d73c","tid":2347101,"uid":48409,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T04:11:23.000Z","msg":"其實係咪當咗樓豬聖女？<br />\n如果你平時都係懶大方咁<br />\n乜嘢都「唔緊要啦！」「無所謂啦！」「唔駛理我啦！」<br />\n我係你男朋友都放你響最尾<br />\n反正你最易話圍<br />\n不過到你發脾氣嘅時候<br />\n條仔就會覺得你唔體諒"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T04:31:17.000Z","msg":"我唔想佢因為我一個人而犧牲同班frd一齊玩嘅時間 咁難得約到 冇可能我一句我想你陪我 就放棄班朋友架嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 至少我自己係咁諗<br />\n所以重要日子你冇陪我唔緊要 但平時冇得見個陣 起碼都抽一兩晚係唔同frd打機陪下我啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢唔係囉"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T04:34:04.000Z","msg":"我開頭都係咁諗，所以我會話無所謂唔緊要啦你去啦，但倒頭自己係到唔開心，覺得佢去咗玩無陪我，愈諗就愈嬲，最後又係嗌交/自己係到唔開心<br />\n<br />\n佢話如果真係介意就直接講，唔好講完唔介意轉就又嚟嬲，佢會更加嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7171672f6c1b7d5a90b440ed415098ed69a2a4b","tid":2347101,"uid":209446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9e6e207fa2253fc130aa98102800dc80be672d92","tid":2347101,"uid":23069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"08caaaae00f37176e5d95fad04913bd3cb0e3f30","tid":2347101,"uid":353924,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"448fb328e1d5886cb19f6a12d9f4445377159901","tid":2347101,"uid":23069,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T03:18:32.000Z","msg":"其實佢凌晨個陣已經同我講左分手<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唉屌 聖誕正日佢講左次分手 依家2020年最後一日都要咁...<br />\n不過唔關倒數佢唔陪我嘅事<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T03:24:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bnpZzvu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbnpZzvu.jpg&h=f4211d1c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n佢可以用好多藉口去同你分手<br />\n但係其實佢都係得一個原因<br />\n佢唔愛你了<br />\n要識得放手，愛自己呀絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申:過來人"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T03:31:06.000Z","msg":"多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />睇到張圖覺得好笑又好想喊<br />\n我都成日同自己講要愛多啲自己 但好似都做唔到<br />\n佢依家掛住打機都冇乜點理到我 我黎M都冇問下我有冇事個啲 鬧交個陣佢仲話係咪黎M就大晒個啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />其實我都係想佢關心一下我 唔好淨係同frd打機就唔理我"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T05:14:18.000Z","msg":"我覺得你可以先同你男朋友溝通咗先<br />\n依家地位 阿媽》朋友〉愛人<br />\n可能佢feel唔到你既委屈<br />\n真係觀念唔啱/唔愛嘅先分手"},{"pid":"d210861769f8306239796115a526793afcc28911","tid":2347101,"uid":14327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T07:07:34.000Z","msg":"Dls 以為自己開post<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0b3edbb1aef387cdea0e7028426ae4cfcd95645","tid":2347101,"uid":48409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aae49b4bfce884a2f0132c56f600b0307612bf35","tid":2347101,"uid":189222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b517f138cad61d927c7c0436b91fcc847ae9e01d","tid":2347101,"uid":23069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0bf72c88db6d2780b4e9a75b9db3dfb20006